2. cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) - The paper discusses the development of methods for community detection, which involves the use of various algorithms and heuristics. 
3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper involves the optimization of an objective function to capture the communities of the network, which is a common technique in machine learning. 
4. cs.SD (Software Engineering) - The paper discusses the implementation of the community detection algorithm and the analysis of its performance, which are relevant topics in software engineering. 
5. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) - The paper deals with the analysis of the community structure of a network, which is a topic related to networking and internet architecture.
